<i>adverb</i>: 찍찍 [찍찍], 찍 [찍], 짝짝 [짝짝], 발칵 [발칵], 맹렬히 [맹ː녈히], 막 [막], 냅다 [냅따], 격렬히 [경녈히] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>찍찍 [찍찍]</dt><br>
<dd>1. haphazardly</dd><br>
<dd>줄이나 획, 글씨 등을 되는 대로 마구 긋거나 쓰는 소리. 또는 그 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word used to describe rough, uncontrolled strokes of a pen or brush, or such a motion.</dd><br>
<dd>2. violently; roughly</dd><br>
<dd>종이나 천 등을 되는 대로 마구 찢는 소리. 또는 그 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word used to describe the sound made when one tears a piece of paper, cloth, etc., to shreds, or such a motion.</dd><br>
<dd>3. sluggishly</dd><br>
<dd>신 등을 바닥에 끌며 걷는 소리. 또는 그 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word used to describe the sound made when one walks, dragging one's shoes, or such a motion.</dd><br>
<dt>찍 [찍]</dt><br>
<dd>1. swiftly; energetically</dd><br>
<dd>줄이나 선을 세게 한 번 긋는 소리. 또는 그 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word used to describe one quick stroke of a pen or brush, or such a motion.</dd><br>
<dd>2. vigorously; violently</dd><br>
<dd>종이나 천 등을 세게 찢는 소리. 또는 그 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word used to describe the sound made when one tears a piece of paper, cloth, etc., violently, or such a motion.</dd><br>
<dt>짝짝 [짝짝]</dt><br>
<dd>1. haphazardly</dd><br>
<dd>줄이나 획을 함부로 긋는 소리. 또는 그 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word used to describe rough, uncontrolled strokes of a pen or brush, or such a motion.</dd><br>
<dd>2. violently; roughly</dd><br>
<dd>종이나 천 등을 마구 찢는 소리. 또는 그 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word used to describe the sound made when one tears a piece of paper, cloth, etc., to shreds, or such a motion.</dd><br>
<dd>3. sluggishly</dd><br>
<dd>신발 등을 가볍게 끌며 걷는 소리. 또는 그 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word used to describe the sound made when one walks, dragging one's shoes lightly, or such a motion.</dd><br>
<dt>발칵 [발칵]</dt><br>
<dd>1. in a fit of rage</dd><br>
<dd>갑자기 화를 내는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of getting angry suddenly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. in a turmoil</dd><br>
<dd>뜻밖에 어떤 일이 벌어져서 갑자기 온통 소란해지거나 야단스러워지는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being in uproar or commotion as something happens unexpectedly.</dd><br>
<dd>3. violently; in the manner of bursting open</dd><br>
<dd>갑자기 문을 열거나 문이 열리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner that someone opens the door or the door is opened suddenly.</dd><br>
<dt>맹렬히 [맹ː녈히]</dt><br>
<dd>violently; wildly</dd><br>
<dd>기운이나 기세가 세차고 사납게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner that energy or force is fierce and strong.</dd><br>
<dt>막 [막]</dt><br>
<dd>1. violently; wildly</dd><br>
<dd>아주 심하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Very severely, roughly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. recklessly; roughly</dd><br>
<dd>아무렇게나 함부로.</dd><br>
<dd>In a careless and reckless manner.</dd><br>
<dt>냅다 [냅따]</dt><br>
<dd>hard; violently</dd><br>
<dd>몹시 세차고 빠르게 갑자기.</dd><br>
<dd>In a very fierce, quick, and sudden manner.</dd><br>
<dt>격렬히 [경녈히]</dt><br>
<dd>violently; fiercely</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동 등이 몹시 거칠고 세차게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a very rough and strong manner in speaking or behaving.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>